{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-plugin-eslint","description":"Gatsby plugin to add support for ESLint","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin","eslint"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"mongkuen","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/6265f40828cde9c50f569217ebabe0a9"},"repository":{"url":"https://github.com/mongkuen/gatsby-plugin-eslint"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-plugin-eslint\"><a href=\"#gatsby-plugin-eslint\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-plugin-eslint</h1>\n<p>Adds ESLint to your Gatsby dev environment, maintaining code quality as you develop.</p>\n<h2 id=\"install\"><a href=\"#install\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Install the <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-plugin-eslint</code> plugin:</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save-dev gatsby-plugin-eslint</code></p>\n<p>or</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add --dev gatsby-plugin-eslint</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Install <a href=\"https://eslint.org/\">ESLint</a> and <a href=\"https://github.com/webpack-contrib/eslint-loader\"><code class=\"language-text\">eslint-loader</code></a>:</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save-dev eslint eslint-loader</code></p>\n<p>or</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add --dev eslint eslint-loader</code></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"usage\"><a href=\"#usage\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Usage</h2>\n<p>Add into <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// gatsby-config.js</span>\n\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">'gatsby-plugin-eslint'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>If no options are specified, the plugin defaults to:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Lint <code class=\"language-text\">.js</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">.jsx</code> files.</li>\n<li>Exclude <code class=\"language-text\">node_modules</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">.cache</code>, and <code class=\"language-text\">public</code> folders from linting.</li>\n<li>Default <a href=\"https://github.com/webpack-contrib/eslint-loader#options\">ESLint-Loader</a> options.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>You can specify your own linting filetypes, exclusions, and <a href=\"https://github.com/webpack-contrib/eslint-loader#options\">ESLint-Loader options</a>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// gatsby-config.js</span>\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'gatsby-plugin-eslint'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        test<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token regex\">/\\.js$|\\.jsx$/</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        exclude<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token regex\">/(node_modules|cache|public)/</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          emitWarning<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          failOnError<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h2 id=\"configuring-eslint\"><a href=\"#configuring-eslint\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Configuring ESLint</h2>\n<p>You’re free to install your own ESLint plugins and rules. Here are 2 easy ways to start linting:</p>\n<h3 id=\"basic-code-classlanguage-texteslint-plugin-reactcode-linting\"><a href=\"#basic-code-classlanguage-texteslint-plugin-reactcode-linting\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Basic <a href=\"https://github.com/yannickcr/eslint-plugin-react\"><code class=\"language-text\">eslint-plugin-react</code></a> Linting</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Follow <a href=\"https://github.com/yannickcr/eslint-plugin-react\"><code class=\"language-text\">eslint-plugin-react</code></a> plugin installation procedures:</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save-dev babel-eslint eslint-plugin-import eslint-plugin-react</code></p>\n<p>or</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add --dev babel-eslint eslint-plugin-import eslint-plugin-react</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Add <code class=\"language-text\">.eslintrc</code> file to project root:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"parser\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"babel-eslint\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"rules\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"strict\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"extends\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"eslint:recommended\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"plugin:react/recommended\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"airbnbs-code-classlanguage-texteslint-config-airbnbcode-linting\"><a href=\"#airbnbs-code-classlanguage-texteslint-config-airbnbcode-linting\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>AirBnB’s <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/eslint-config-airbnb\"><code class=\"language-text\">eslint-config-airbnb</code></a> Linting</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Follow <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/eslint-config-airbnb\"><code class=\"language-text\">eslint-config-airbnb</code></a> plugin installation procedures:</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save-dev eslint-config-airbnb eslint-plugin-import eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y eslint-plugin-react</code></p>\n<p>or</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add --dev eslint-config-airbnb eslint-plugin-import eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y eslint-plugin-react</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Add <code class=\"language-text\">.eslintrc</code> file to project root:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"extends\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"airbnb\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n</li>\n</ol>","timeToRead":2}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-plugin-eslint/","id":"89017e21-e1e0-5e52-96b4-b4532bf52ada"}}